  <h1>Heart's United - Child Sexual Abuse and Exploitation (CSAE) Policy</h1>

  <p>
    Heart's United is committed to protecting the safety and dignity of all individuals, especially children. We maintain a strict zero-tolerance policy against Child Sexual Abuse and Exploitation (CSAE).
  </p>

  <h2>Our Commitments</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>We prohibit any content, images, videos, or messages that promote or depict CSAE.</li>
    <li>We take swift action to remove any suspected CSAE content from our platform.</li>
    <li>We permanently ban accounts found violating this policy.</li>
    <li>We report all relevant incidents to appropriate law enforcement and child protection organizations.</li>
    <li>We comply with all applicable international and local laws including the UN Convention on the Rights of the Child and COPPA.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Reporting</h2>
